      "writtenOn": "2026-06-02T10:30:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "No, this is not related to BlueZ.\n\nThese constants correspond to D-Bus interfaces defined by neard,\nwhich is the NFC manager in the Linux NFC stack. For example,\n\"org.neard.Record\" is the interface used by neard to expose\nNDEF records over D-Bus.\n\nThis code simply consumes those interfaces to retrieve NFC tag\nrecords, rather than defining a new protocol or reusing anything\nfrom BlueZ.",
      "parentUuid": "84724949_6c547202",
      "revId": "024c47f3d40188bb94229103c7063e977fdebfb1",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
